    {
      "id": "PopularPost346459",
      "post_content": "This card is a huge liability. When would you ever want [completely](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=129588) [free](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=1494) [opponent-controlled](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=46724) [discard](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=12449)?  \n  \nIf you're really concerned about the opponent actually using Scandalmonger against you, use madness. They won't waste a spark of mana on Scandalmonger and you've essentially got an inverse [Azure Mage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Azure Mage).",
      "posted_by": "MacBizzle",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost346459\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">This card is a huge liability. When would you ever want <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"129588\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=129588\">completely</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"1494\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=1494\">free</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"46724\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=46724\">opponent-controlled</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"12449\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=12449\">discard</a>?<br/><br/>If you're really concerned about the opponent actually using Scandalmonger against you, use madness. They won't waste a spark of mana on Scandalmonger and you've essentially got an inverse <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Azure Mage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Azure Mage\">Azure Mage</a>.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '346459'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46803\">MacBizzle</span>\r\n                                (10/17/2013 11:28:58 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\